'''Zila''' was a resort town on the shore of the [[Locura Ocean]] on the planet of [[Garos IV]]. [[Baro|Counselor Baro]], along with many other high ranking [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] officials stationed on the planet lived in Zila. [[Mount Berin]] was located on the outskirts of the city.

